-- Sarkozy Names Kosciusko-Morizet for Campaign, AFP Reports
-- B y   A n d r e w   R o b e r t s
-- 2012-02-18T12:31:28Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-18/sarkozy-names-kosciusko-morizet-for-campaign-afp-reports.html
French President  Nicolas Sarkozy 
named Nathalie Kosciusko-Morizet as spokeswoman for his
electoral campaign and said the Environment Minister would quit
government in a few days, Agence France-Presse reported.  To contact the reporter on this story:
